<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting VespaVerse</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #0a0b1e;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1b2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .message {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .contact-info h3 {
            color: #6366f1;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            color: #a1a1aa;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ec4899 0%, #6366f1 100%);
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .timeline {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .timeline-item {
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .timeline-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .timeline-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        
        .social-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 8px;
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 24px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #a1a1aa;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content {
                padding: 24px 20px;
            }
            
            .timeline {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">V</div>
            <h1>Thank You!</h1>
            <p>We've received your message and will respond soon</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hi {{firstName}},
            </div>
            
            <p>Thank you for reaching out to VespaVerse! We're excited to learn about your project and explore how we can help bring your vision to life.</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h3>Your Contact Details</h3>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Reference ID:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">#{{contactId}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Submitted:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{formatDate createdAt}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if service}}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Service Interest:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{service}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if budget}}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Budget Range:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{budget}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
                <p>Our team will review your requirements and get back to you with a personalized response.</p>
                
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-icon">1</div>
                        <div class="timeline-text">Review<br>0-2 hours</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-icon">2</div>
                        <div class="timeline-text">Response<br>Within 24h</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-icon">3</div>
                        <div class="timeline-text">Consultation<br>Within 48h</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p><strong>Your Message:</strong></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 12px; font-style: italic;">"{{message}}"</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>In the meantime, feel free to explore our recent projects and client success stories:</p>
            
            <div class="cta">
                <a href="{{baseUrl}}/projects" class="button">View Our Work</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any urgent questions, don't hesitate to call us at <strong>+1 (555) 123-4567</strong> or email us directly at <strong>hello@vespaverse.com</strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="#" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
                <a href="#" class="social-link">GitHub</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} VespaVerse. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{baseUrl}}/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="{{baseUrl}}/terms">Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>